title: Family honors late daughter, sister with festival
text:
Published By: Florida Today: Life - Today 
On Saturday, the Kabboord family will host its 13th annual Crystal's Day from 11 a.m. to 3 p.m. at Gleason Park in Indian Harbour Beach.
